      "source": [
        "## Debug Model Loading in /predict Endpoint - Findings\n",
        "\n",
        "### Investigation into 'Models not loaded' issue:\n",
        "\n",
        "1.  **FastAPI Server Setup Output (cell `d8ab6357`):**\n",
        "    Upon reviewing the output from the execution of the FastAPI server setup, the following messages confirm successful model loading:\n",
        "    ```\n",
        "    Attempting to load models at startup...\n",
        "    ✅ Successfully loaded model from newsbot_classifier.pkl\n",
        "    ✅ Successfully loaded vectorizer from newsbot_vectorizer.pkl\n",
        "    ```\n",
        "    This clearly indicates that the `newsbot_classifier.pkl` model and `newsbot_vectorizer.pkl` were successfully loaded during the application's startup process, addressing the previous 'Models not loaded' concern.\n",
