        "Base URL for API testing: http://0.0.0.0:40315\n",
        "\n",
        "--- Testing /predict endpoint ---\n",
        "Testing with a sport article...\n",
        "Response for sport article: {'predicted_category': 'sport'}\n",
        "Testing with a business article...\n",
        "Response for business article: {'predicted_category': 'business'}\n",
