        "## Generate Python Script for API Testing\n",
        "\n",
        "### Subtask:\n",
        "Create a Python script that uses the `requests` library to make POST requests to the `/predict` endpoint and a GET request to the `/metrics` endpoint. The script should use the dynamically assigned `FASTAPI_PORT` variable and include sample text for prediction, printing the responses for both endpoints.\n"
