      "source": [
        "## Summary:\n",
        "\n",
        "### Q&A\n",
        "The immediate next task to summarize insights gained from the most frequent terms per category, highlighting their domain-specific context, has been completed.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Data Analysis Key Findings\n",
        "*   A Python function, `get_most_frequent_terms`, was successfully implemented and executed to extract the most frequent terms per category based on mean TF-IDF scores.\n",
        "*   The function identified the top 10 most frequent terms (including n-grams) for each of the five categories:\n",
        "    *   **BUSINESS:** 'bn', 'said', 'firm', 'company', 'market', 'bank', 'growth', 'year', 'economy', 'sale'\n",
        "    *   **TECH:** 'mobile', 'phone', 'people', 'said', 'technology', 'game', 'user', 'service', 'software', 'computer'\n",
