        "*   **Potential Overlaps:** The term 'said' appears frequently across all categories, indicating its generic nature in news reporting and its limited discriminative power. More interestingly, the term **'game' appears in both 'TECH' and 'SPORT'** categories.\n",
        "    *   In 'TECH', 'game' likely refers to video games or gaming technology.\n",
        "    *   In 'SPORT', 'game' refers to athletic competitions.\n",
