        "## Summary of `main.py` Review\n",
        "\n",
        "### Configuration and Setup:\n",
        "*   **Model Paths**: The `MODEL_PATH` and `VECTORIZER_PATH` are explicitly set to `/content/newsbot_classifier.pkl` and `/content/newsbot_vectorizer.pkl`, indicating that the FastAPI application is designed to load these specific files from the `/content/` directory. This is consistent with where the models were saved in previous steps.\n",
        "*   **NLTK Resources**: The code includes `nltk.download` calls for various resources (`punkt`, `punkt_tab`, `stopwords`, `wordnet`, `omw-1.4`) to ensure the preprocessing functions have all necessary dependencies.\n",
