        "## Train and Evaluate Classifier with BERT Embeddings\n",
        "\n",
        "### Subtask:\n",
        "Split the dataset with the new combined features (including BERT embeddings) into training and testing sets. Train a new classifier (e.g., RandomForestClassifier) and evaluate its performance using a classification report and confusion matrix, with a particular focus on the 'tech' category.\n"
      ]
